In the example you've provided, the handleSave function is defined in the EditMenuContainer component and is invoked when the <button> element is clicked. To allow a child component, such as EditMenu, to invoke the handleSave function when a button is clicked within it, you can pass the handleSave function as a prop to the child component.Here's an example of how you can pass the handleSave function as a prop to the EditMenu component:Copy codereturn (
	<>
		<EditMenu 
          editMenu={editMenu.system} 
